        "pubDate": "2026-04-13T17:15:16Z",
        "description": "Unconventional superconductivity is generally expected to be strongly suppressed by nonmagnetic disorder, as captured by Abrikosov--Gor'kov (AG) theory. However, several materials, including transition metal dichalcogenides, exhibit signatures of unconventional pairing despite relatively high resist",
        "title_cn": "减少非常规超导体中延伸性疾病的配对断裂：对4Hb-TaS的影响$_2 $"
      },
      {
        "title": "An analogue of irreducible cuspidal representations for the group $PGL(2)$ over a two-dimensional local field",
        "link": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2604.11735v1",
        "pubDate": "2026-04-13T17:13:56Z",
        "description": "Let $F$ be a local non-archimedian field of odd residue characteristic and let $G=PGL(2)$. In this paper we study an analog of irreducible cuspidal representations of the group $G(F)$ when $F$ is replaced by the field $K=F((t))$. The story turns out to be similar to the classical case, but also with",
        "title_cn": "在二维局部场上群$ PGL (2) $的不可约的尖端表示的模拟"
      },
      {
