        "description": "Precise mass and radius measurements of small, transitional exoplanets, such as super-Earths and sub-Neptunes, are essential to constrain their bulk density and formation history, serving as prerequisites for atmospheric characterization. The ArMS Large Programme, carried out within GAPS using the H",
        "title_cn": "TNG的GAPS计划。LXXIII.确认热亚海王星TOI-4602 b （ HD 25295 b ） ，这是未来大气表征的关键目标"
